a very great statement “Still I am doubting.”

00:38:51.612 --> 00:38:57.652
Is that the sign of wisdom? What are you doubting?

00:38:59.292 --> 00:39:03.292
What have you found out so far?

00:39:03.892 --> 00:39:07.092
From where does this come?

00:39:07.332 --> 00:39:12.812
Is Mr. Ego, about which I have given lectures after lectures.

00:39:13.132 --> 00:39:16.932
Is Mr. Ego that is doubting it?

00:39:17.132 --> 00:39:19.492
Because he doesn’t want you to find the absolute.

00:39:19.692 --> 00:39:23.092
You are identified with your Ego,

00:39:23.292 --> 00:39:25.852
and you do not want to find it because,

00:39:26.052 --> 00:39:29.412
this Mr. Ego has been guiding your life throughout,

00:39:29.652 --> 00:39:33.652
and now [YOU DON’T …del] you want to doubt. Doubt what?

00:39:34.652 --> 00:39:41.132
What are you doubting? You felt the cool breeze, all right?

00:39:41.412 --> 00:39:42.572
Sit down then.

00:39:42.772 --> 00:39:45.852
It would be something like somebody entering into a college,

00:39:46.052 --> 00:39:50.852
university, and they are going sitting down firstly there,

00:39:51.092 --> 00:39:54.812
teacher says “Now, this is the diagram, I give you.”

00:39:55.012 --> 00:40:00.172
