00:40:36.812 --> 00:40:40.412
Like somebody says “I am going to teach you how to fly.”

00:40:40.652 --> 00:40:43.612
They’re absolutely ready for that.

00:40:43.812 --> 00:40:46.692
They’ll pay money, and not doubt, even a bit,

00:40:46.892 --> 00:40:49.812
that the fellow who is propagating is he flying?

00:40:50.012 --> 00:40:51.532
Have you seen him flying anywhere?

00:40:51.732 --> 00:40:54.332
Please at least ask that person to fly.

00:40:54.532 --> 00:40:57.612
They will see the Kundalini rising with their eyes,

00:40:57.812 --> 00:41:00.652
they will see it pulsating, rising, breaking here,

00:41:00.852 --> 00:41:03.212
still they’ll sit down and say “I am doubting.”

00:41:03.412 --> 00:41:07.732
Now who are you? How far have you reached?

00:41:08.012 --> 00:41:12.012
Why are you doubting? What are you doubting?

00:41:12.852 --> 00:41:15.292
What have you known so far about yourself?

00:41:15.492 --> 00:41:20.772
Now, humble down yourself at this point Humble down in your heart.

00:41:21.012 --> 00:41:27.412
“No I have not known myself. I have to know myself.

00:41:28.132 --> 00:41:31.772
I have not known myself, I haven’t got the absolute.

00:41:31.972 --> 00:41:33.892
With what instruments I am doubting?”

00:41:34.092 --> 00:41:37.692
This is one of the greatest hurdles of Kundalini awakening

00:41:37.892 --> 00:41:42.652
and in after awakening, called as Samshaya.

